{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0\b\fs40 Cut Time on Selected Tracks — Shuffle Style\par}
{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0 Perform Pro Tools–style Shuffle editing, but restricted to the tracks you select.\par}

{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0 This script removes a defined time range and automatically closes the gap only on selected tracks, leaving all others intact.\par}

{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0 Features:\par}
{\pard\ql\f0\sa0\li360\fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Razor Area or Time Selection support,\par}
{\pard\ql\f0\sa0\li360\fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab True shuffle-style ripple closing on selected tracks only,\par}
{\pard\ql\f0\sa0\li360\fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Non-destructive editing for unselected tracks,\par}
{\pard\ql\f0\sa0\li360\fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ImGui interface for clear visual feedback.\par}

{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0 Ideal for precise Pro Tools–like editing workflows within REAPER.\par}
{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0 Developed by Mariow & Fernsehmuell.\par}
